in Information Technology in Asia.
<LI><A HREF="http://www.moe.ac.sg/">http://www.moe.ac.sg/</A><BR>
The home page of Singapore's Ministry of Education.  Contains 
information about the education system, education standards, and new 
developments. 
<LI><A HREF="http://www.ncb.gov.sg/it2k/it2k.html">http://www.ncb.gov.sg/it2k/it2k.html</A><BR>
A description of the IT2000 Vision.  Includes an explanation for its 
development and a discussion about related issues. 
</OL></P>


